{{Location map|Canada New Brunswick|lat=46.9687|long=-64.8236|width=200|caption=Location of Pointe-Sapin in [[New Brunswick]]|label=Pointe-Sapin}} '''Pointe-Sapin''' is a [[List of communities in New Brunswick|settlement]] on the Northern coast of [[New Brunswick]] on the Northumberland Strait in the Gulf of the St. Lawrence. Pointe Sapin lies in the Atlantic Time Zone (AST/ADT) and observes daylight saving time

